          "fill": "#444444",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "✅ 文章 CRUD（草稿/发布/撤回/删除）\n✅ 双库分离（制作库 + 线上库）\n✅ 文章缓存（Redis Cache-Aside）\n✅ 读者公开文章列表 + 详情页\n✅ 文章摘要（Content 前128字）\n✅ 分页查询 + 全量列表\n✅ 响应式适配（桌面 + 移动端）\n✅ Modal.confirm 二次确认\n✅ camelCase 统一字段命名\n✅ Result JSON 统一响应格式",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
          "fontSize": 12
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "id": "o33IH",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "height": 1,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "center",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "#E5E7EB"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "IN8FK",
          "fill": "#6366F1",
          "content": "页面清单（7页）",
          "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "s7MzM",
          "fill": "#444444",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "1. 文章广场 /feed（公开）\n2. 文章阅读页 /article/[id]（公开）\n3. 我的文章 /article/list（需登录）\n4. 写文章 /article/edit（需登录）\n5. 编辑文章 /article/edit/[id]（需登录）\n6. 首页 /（需登录）\n7. 确认弹窗（撤回/删除）",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
          "fontSize": 12
        },
